    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I have been tinkering with ipython+emacs+mpl on windows for many moons.\nemacs 24.5.1 - emacs 25.x does not work\n\nThe best setup I have found that works practically is\n(setq\n python-shell-interpreter \"C:\\Anaconda2\\python.exe\"\n python-shell-interpreter-args \"-i C:\\Anaconda2\\Scripts\\jupyter-console-script.py\")\n\nwith these versions at best!  Anything higher is a tale of woe.\nipython 4.1.2 py27_1\njupyter 1.0.0 py27_3\njupyter_client 4.3.0 py27_0\njupyter_console 4.1.1 py27_0\njupyter_core 4.1.1 py27_0\nmatplotlib 1.5.1 np111py27_0\n\nUse %pylab to get plotting to work\n\nIf anyone can get beyond these versions please let us know.\nThanks!\n"
